{"type":null,"faqId":46065,"title":"手机仅充电模式可以连接hisuite吗？Hisuite连接失败怎么办？如何安装驱动？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>仅充电模式不支持hisuite连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1、手机默认出厂模式为Hisuite模式(移动版本要求默认为Google，插卡激活后也会自动变成Hisuite模式)，USB端口为管理文件模式（MTP）；</span>\n<br>\n<span>2、请检查端口驱动是否自动安装成功，如果驱动装载失败，请将电脑驱动卸载更新；</span>\n<br>\n<span>3、插上USB端口，选择照片/文件管理模式，查看我的电脑上的驱动盘符，双击HisuiteDownLoader.exe。自动连接在线下载安装</span>\n<br>\n<span>或者进入官网手动下载驱动安装，地址为“</span><a href=\"http://emui.huawei.com/plugin.php?id=hwdownload\"><span>http://emui.huawei.com/plugin.php?id=hwdownload</span></a><span>“，选择刷机工具--Hisuite下载</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=170477\" style=\"width:6.7618055in;height:3.0472221in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><br>\n<span>4、驱动安装成功，打开如果提示失败，电脑端会有帮助提示如何打开USB调试功能进行操作；</span>\n<br>\n<span>5、如果还未成功连接请检查系统设置--安全--PC助手（HiSuite）是否打开；</span>\n<br>\n<span>6、仍未成功连接到手机助手，请选择端口为照片/文件管理模式；</span>\n<br>\n<span>7、用户也可通过选择端口模式中的帮助进行电脑驱动安装。</span>\n<br>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":1,"unUseful":11,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1845","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444375613000,"seriesProductName":"","visitedTimes":3482,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"hisuite,仅充电","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}